Minor feature support
---------------------
Hadoop
- namenode failover w/ shared dir mechanism
- start w/ 2.1.1-beta 
Ganglia
- if user wants aid in monitoring
hdfs over lustre/networkfs
- stripe over multiple networked file systems
- higher availability, maybe faster speed, etc.

Setup-script
- generate script that user can run to setup environment before running job
  - e.g. set HADOOP_CONF_DIR, HADOOP_HOME, etc.

Hbase
- thrift server?
- multiple masters
- region merge script

Spark
- multiple masters
